gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 106, Magic 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Magic, 106-103. D'Angelo Russell recorded 28 points, eight assists, and two rebounds for the Lakers, with Anthony Davis adding 26 points, 19 rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Gary Harris tallied 17 points, three rebounds, and three assists for the Magic in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Magic fall to 2-1.
